(58, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 32, 'Portable Air Cooler Fan with Heater and Humidifier Function - Color: Gray', 'portable-air-cooler-fan-with-heater-and-humidifier-function-color-gray', 'local', 'D681-EP23664', 'Portable Air Cooler Fan with Heater and Humidifier Function - Color: Gray', 'Portable Air Cooler Fan with Heater and Humidifier Function - Color: Gray', 'Portable Air Cooler Fan with Heater and Humidifier Function - Color: Gray', 'Specifications: Color: As pics show Net weight: 17 lbs Voltage: 110V 60Hz Fan mode power: 75W Heating mode power: 2000W(High)/ 1000W(Low) Timer: 8 hour Water tank capacity: 7L Fan mode: Normal/Natural/Sleeping Fan speed: Low/Middle/High Heating temperature: Low/High Overall dimension: 15\" (L) x 11\" (W) x 29\" (H) Air flow: 334 CFM Box Qty: 1(May vary by batch)Package includes: 1 x Air cooler & heater 2 x Ice crystal box<br />Measurement: 32.09\" x 16.34\" x 12.80\"<br /><p>The indoor portable evaporative air cooler and heater which distributes cool air through the honeycomb cooling media while the dust filter cleanses the air.</p> <p>It\'s non-compressor system cools naturally efficiently and inexpensively without power-hungry components. It is heated by ptc heater high efficiency of conversion between electricity and heat rapid heating. This evaporative air cooler heater humidifier and fan is versatile lightweight and economical. It can also be used as a air purifier because of its anion generator. The remote control allows you to easily change settings. And this air cooler and heater easily rolls from room to room for use anywhere in your house or office.</p> <p>The indoor portable evaporative air cooler and heater. Don\'t hesitate to buy it.</p> <ul> <li>Can be used as...', 'Specifications: Color: As pics show Net weight: 17 lbs Voltage: 110V  60Hz Fan mode power: 75W Heating mode power: 2000W(High)/ 1000W(Low) Timer: 8 hour Water tank capacity: 7L Fan mode: Normal/Natural/Sleeping Fan speed: Low/Middle/High Heating temperature: Low/High Overall dimension: 15\" (L) x 11\" (W) x 29\" (H) Air flow: 334 CFM Box Qty: 1(May vary by batch)Package includes: 1 x Air cooler & heater 2 x Ice crystal box<br />Measurement: 32.09\" x 16.34\" x 12.80\"<br /><p>The indoor portable evaporative air cooler and heater which distributes cool air through the honeycomb cooling media while the dust filter cleanses the air.</p>  <p>It\'s non-compressor system cools naturally  efficiently and inexpensively without power-hungry components. It is heated by ptc heater  high efficiency of conversion between electricity and heat  rapid heating. This evaporative air cooler  heater  humidifier  and fan is versatile  lightweight and economical. It can also be used as a air purifier because of its anion generator. The remote control allows you to easily change settings. And this air cooler and heater easily rolls from room to room for use anywhere in your house or office.</p>   <p>The indoor portable evaporative air cooler and heater. Don\'t hesitate to buy it.</p>  <ul> <li>Can be used as air cooler  heater  humidifier  fan  air purifier</li> <li>Ideal for using in home  office  dormitory and so on</li> <li>Utilizes a superb honeycomb cooling pad that ensures a high level of cooling</li> <li>Increase temperature by efficient ptc heater</li> <li>Removable  washable filter prevents bacteria  dust and other air borne particles</li> <li>Anion purifies and sterilizes air by generating negative ion</li> <li>8 Hour timer  swing feature  3 fan modes and speeds to customize your cooling</li> <li>2 Ice-crystal boxes enhance cooling performance</li> <li>User-friendly led control panel</li> <li>19.5\" Far-range remote control  receive at 60 degree wide angle</li> <li>4 Caster wheels make it easy to move from room to room</li> </ul>', 294.99, 500, '1759574730_68e0facac85c0.jpg', NULL, '{\"Brand\":\"XMCSMY\",\"UPC\":\"6933315536350\",\"Weight\":\"22.49\",\"Condition\":\"N\"}', 1, '2025-08-28 12:10:43', '2025-10-04 16:15:30'),
