untries need to take 20-60 days.</span></span></strong></div><div><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:verdana, geneva, sans-serif\">If you need the goods urgently, please choose DHL/FedEx/UPS/TNT/ EMS, usually takes 3-7days,EMS need to take 5-15 days.</span></span></strong></div><h1><strong><span style=\"font-size:26px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(192, 0, 0)\"><span style=\"font-family:verdana, geneva, sans-serif\">About payment</span></span></span></strong></h1><div><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:verdana, geneva, sans-serif\">Escrow is our preferable payment method, we also accept other payments by Visa, Credit-card, T/T, Western union, Money gram, etc.</span></span></strong></div><div><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:verdana, geneva, sans-serif\">When we receive your payment note for the order, we will arrange shippment.</span></span></strong></div><div><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:verdana, geneva, sans-serif\">Please make sure to confirm the order when you receive the items in a good condition, because when you place a order, your money is transferring into the Escrow, not our account. If you don\'t  receive the goods, we will not get your money, don\'t worry, we will extend the time until you receive them.</span></span></strong></div><h1><strong><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(192, 0, 0)\"><span style=\"font-family:verdana, geneva, sans-serif\">Feedback</span></span></span></strong></h1><div><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:verdana, geneva, sans-serif\">Dear friend, if you are satisfied with our service, please leave us a positive feedback. And we will do the same for you. If you have any question, please contact us first, and we will reply all the questions within 24 hours</span></span></strong></div><div> </div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></di