(68, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 32, 'Trexonic Portable TV+DVD Player with Color TFT LED Screen and USB/HD/AV Inputs', 'trexonic-portable-tvdvd-player-with-color-tft-led-screen-and-usbhdav-inputs', 'local', 'D970-TR-D125', 'Trexonic Portable TV+DVD Player with Color TFT LED Screen and USB/HD/AV Inputs', 'Trexonic Portable TV+DVD Player with Color TFT LED Screen and USB/HD/AV Inputs', 'Trexonic Portable TV+DVD Player with Color TFT LED Screen and USB/HD/AV Inputs', 'Enjoy all your favorite movies and television shows on the go with this Trexonic 12.5 Inch Portable DVD player. Take all your shows on the go thanks to its long lasting rechargeable battery. <br>The TFT high resolution screen swivels and tilts for perfect enjoyment at any angle. The wide 12.5 inch display ensures clear and beautiful images.<br>It supports several formats so you can easily enjoy long road trips, camping, flying and movie nights whether on a flash drive, memory card or disc.<br><br>Enjoy Your Entertainment Longer! This unit offers you a rechargeable battery so you don\'t have to be tied down to a charging cable.<br><br>Charge On the Go! You don\'t have to worry about leaving entertainment behind when you can easily take it along for the ride! With the included Car Adapter, you can enjoy your favorite movies while you are out and about. <br><br>Find Your Own Angle! This convenient Portable DVD player offers you a 90 Degree rotation to the left and a 180 Degree rotation the right, allowing you to fully turn your screen, and even close the unit with the screen pointing out. <br><br>Play It Your Way! Choose the right input for you: SD / USB / Earphones...', 'Enjoy all your favorite movies and television shows on the go with this Trexonic 12.5 Inch Portable DVD player. Take all your shows on the go thanks to its long lasting rechargeable battery. <br>The TFT high resolution screen swivels and tilts  for perfect enjoyment at any angle. The wide 12.5 inch display ensures clear and beautiful images.<br>It supports several formats so you can easily enjoy long road trips, camping, flying and movie nights whether on a flash drive, memory card or disc.<br><br>Enjoy Your Entertainment Longer! This unit offers you a rechargeable battery so you don\'t have to be tied down to a charging cable.<br><br>Charge On the Go! You don\'t have to worry about leaving entertainment behind when you can easily take it along for the ride! With the included Car Adapter, you can enjoy your favorite movies while you are out and about. <br><br>Find Your Own Angle! This convenient Portable DVD player offers you a 90 Degree rotation to the left and a 180 Degree rotation the right, allowing you to fully turn your screen, and even close the unit with  the screen pointing out. <br><br>Play It Your Way! Choose the right input for you: SD / USB / Earphones Input / AV Input/ AV Output/DC Input<br><br>This unit makes a wonderful gift for your friends and family, coworkers, and anyone with kids who appreciates the power of entertainment! Whether you enjoy this unit in your man cave, on a camping trip, or even during a picnic, you can\'t go wrong with the reliability and quality of Trexonic.<br>WARNING: This product can expose you to chemicals including DEHP, which is known to the State of California to cause cancer and/or reproductive harm. For more information, go to www.P65Warnings.ca.gov.', 199.99, 16, '1759574742_68e0fad6a91c3.jpg', NULL, '{\"Brand\":\"Trexonic\",\"UPC\":\"840191201448\",\"Weight\":\"3.00\",\"Condition\":\"N\"}', 1, '2025-08-28 12:10:58', '2025-10-04 16:15:42'),
(69, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 32, 'Trexonic 14.1 Inch Portable DVD Player with Swivel TFT-LCD Screen and USB,SD,AV Inputs', 'trexonic-141-inch-portable-dvd-player-with-swivel-tft-lcd-screen-and-usbsdav-inputs', 'local', 'D970-TRX-1580', 'Trexonic 14.1 Inch Portable DVD Player with Swivel TFT-LCD Screen and USB,SD,AV Inputs', 'Trexonic 14.1 Inch Portable DVD Player with Swivel TFT-LCD Screen and USB,SD,AV Inputs', 'Trexonic 14.1 Inch Portable DVD Player with Swivel TFT-LCD Screen and USB,SD,AV Inputs', 'Enjoy your movies and other digital files on the go with the Trexonic 14.1 Inch Portable DVD Player with TFT-LCD Screen and USB,SD,AV Inputs. Easily connect it to a television or take it with you wherever you want, thanks to its long-lasting rechargeable battery. The TFT high resolution screen swivels 270° and tilts 180° for perfect enjoyment at any angle and the wide 14\" display ensures clear and beautiful images. It supports several formats so you can enjoy a plethora of different files, whether on a flash drive, memory card or disc. Enjoy Your Entertainment Longer! This unit offers you a rechargeable battery and car adaptor so you don\'t have to be tied down to a charging cable. Choose the right input for you: SD / USB / Earphones Input / AV Input/ AV Output/DC Input and Play It Your Way!<br>WARNING: This product can expose you to chemicals including BBP, which is known to the State of California to cause cancer and/or reproductive harm. For more information, go to www.P65Warnings.ca.gov.', 'Enjoy your movies and other digital files on the go with the Trexonic 14.1 Inch Portable DVD Player with TFT-LCD Screen and USB,SD,AV Inputs. Easily connect it to a television or take it with you wherever you want, thanks to its long-lasting rechargeable battery. The TFT high resolution screen swivels 270° and tilts 180° for perfect enjoyment at any angle and the wide 14\" display ensures clear and beautiful images. It supports several formats so you can enjoy a plethora of dif