(90, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 32, 'Style: Gold - Love Locked Bracelet With A Charm', 'style-gold-love-locked-bracelet-with-a-charm', 'local', 'K290-14091993579555', 'Style: Gold - Love Locked Bracelet With A Charm', 'Style: Gold - Love Locked Bracelet With A Charm', 'Style: Gold - Love Locked Bracelet With A Charm', 'You will be intrigued by its charm...Express undying, unbreakable and unlimited love by gifting this bracelet to your love... Remember your visit together on the Pont des Arts bridge in Paris where you had put a love lock and threw away the key in the Seine river never to find it... Remind your sweetheart again you have Love Locked her with your lifelong commitment with this little token of a charm! DETAILS:It is made in White Gold, Gold and Rose gold plating.It has delicate pave crystals that shine like real diamonds and the pave crystal little lock to express love and add to its charm. This open-ended bracelet measures 7 inches, opens to slip on and locks securely.The bracelets come in White Gold, Gold and Rose gold shades in a gift box for gift giving and safekeeping.Get more, each sold individually.', 'You will be intrigued by its charm...Express undying, unbreakable and unlimited love by gifting this bracelet to your love... Remember your visit together on the Pont des Arts bridge in Paris where you had put a love lock and threw away the key in the Seine river never to find it... Remind your sweetheart again you have Love Locked her with your lifelong commitment with this little token of a charm! DETAILS:It is made in White Gold, Gold and Rose gold plating.It has delicate pave crystals that shine like real diamonds and the pave crystal little lock to express love and add to its charm. This open-ended bracelet measures 7 inches, opens to slip on and locks securely.The bracelets come in White Gold, Gold and Rose gold shades in a gift box for gift giving and safekeeping.Get more, each sold individually.', 129.95, 25, '1759574770_68e0faf21f5c2.jpg', NULL, '{\"Brand\":\"Motormax\",\"UPC\":\"723466562423\",\"Weight\":\"0.13\",\"Condition\":\"N\"}', 1, '2025-08-28 12:11:28', '2025-10-04 16:16:10'),
(91, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 32, 'Ring Color: CLASSIC CHAMPAGNE,Ring Size: 11 - Cocktail & Mocktail Rings CZ Crystals With Ombre Effect', 'ring-color-classic-champagnering-size-11-cocktail-mocktail-rings-cz-crystals-with-ombre-effect', 'local', 'K290-31023126352', 'Ring Color: CLASSIC CHAMPAGNE,Ring Size: 11 - Cocktail & Mocktail Rings CZ Crystals With Ombre Effect', 'Ring Color: CLASSIC CHAMPAGNE,Ring Size: 11 - Cocktail & Mocktail Rings CZ Crystals With Ombre Effect', 'Ring Color: CLASSIC CHAMPAGNE,Ring Size: 11 - Cocktail & Mocktail Rings CZ Crystals With Ombre Effect', 'Invited to a cocktail mock-tail party..?Enjoy company of friends with your shaded rings.. Whatever you are holding in your delicate stem glass, whether it\'s Champagne, Merlot, Rose`or sparkling fruity Wines, will surely resemble with your ring.. Both of them come in such sweet mix of colors, you cannot help enjoy their good company..Say three cheers to Cocktail & Mock-tail!!!DETAILS:It is made of Sterling Silver with CZ crystals in three shades on each ring giving ombre effect.It comes in sizes 6,7,8,9,10,11 and 12.It comes in beautiful colors like Pink Slaty Dog and Spiked CoCo Banana.It comes in a gift box for gift giving and safe keeping.Get more as they are irresistible.. each sold separately.', 'Invited to a cocktail mock-tail party..?Enjoy company of friends with your shaded rings.. Whatever you are holding in your delicate stem glass, whether it\'s Champagne, Merlot, Rose`or sparkling fruity Wines, will surely resemble with your ring.. Both of them come in such sweet mix of colors, you cannot help enjoy their good company..Say three cheers to Cocktail & Mock-tail!!!DETAILS:It is made of Sterling Silver with CZ crystals in three shades on each ring giving ombre effect.It comes in sizes 6,7,8,9,10,11 and 12.It comes in beautiful colors like Pink Slaty Dog and Spiked CoCo Banana.It comes in a gift box for gift giving and safe keeping.Get more as they are irresistible.. each sold separately.', 43.95, 22, '1759574770_68e0faf249bfa.jpg', NULL, '{\"Brand\":\"Motormax\",\"UPC\":\"702921592090\",\"Weight\":\"0.30\",\"Condition\":\"N\"}', 1, '2025-08-28 12:11:28', '2025-10-04 16:16:10'),
(92, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 32, 'Size: Gold,Ring Size: 6 - Ella Eternity Band With 4 Crystals Classic Stackable Ring', 'size-goldring-size-6-ella-eternity-band-with-4-crystals-classic-stackable-ring', 'local', 'K290-32076406096', 'Size: Gold,Ring Size: 6 - Ella Eternity Band With 4 Crystals Classic Stackable Ring', 'Size: Gold,Ring Size: 6 - Ella Eternity Band With 4 Crystals Classic Stackable Ring', 'Size: Gold,Ring Size: 6 - Ella Eternity Band With 4 Crystals Classic Stackable Ring', 'Classic and Delicate.. This eternity band is stackable and smooth, has well-rounded feel inside out and the 4 spaced out crystal stones all around give this ring a brilliance that is here to say in all 4 seasons.. Select it with your special someone and get it for each other to wear them together..Ella..Stay proud of your choice till Eternity..DETAILS:The ring is made of  Yellow Gold plating, Rose Gold Plating and White Gold Plating.It also has 4 little Crystal stones that shine brilliantly.A classic piece of jewelry that feels like a privilege and so comfortable to wear.It comes in Golden Band, Rose Gold Band and  White Gold plated  Band.It comes in sizes 5,6,7,8 AND 9.Great gift as an anniversary band, engagement ring, wedding band or a couple\'s ring just because..Each sold separately.', 'Classic and Delicate.. This eternity band is stackable and smooth, has well-rounded feel inside out and the 4 spaced out crystal stones all around give this ring a brilliance that is here to say in all 4 seasons.. Select it with your special someone and get it for each other to wear them together..Ella..Stay proud of your choice till Eternity..DETAILS:The ring is made of  Yellow Gold plating, Rose Gold Plating and White Gold Plating.It also has 4 little Crystal stones that shine brilliantly.A classic piece of jewelry that feels like a privilege and so comfortable to wear.It comes in Golden Band, Rose Gold Band and  White Gold plated  Band.It comes in sizes 5,6,7,8 AND 9.Great gift as an anniversary band, engagement ring, wedding band or a couple\'s ring just because..Each sold separately.', 29.95, 52, '1759574770_68e0faf25fd38.jpg', NULL, '{\"Brand\":\"Motormax\",\"UPC\":\"702921591475\",\"Weight\":\"0.30\",\"Condition\":\"N\"}', 1, '2025-08-28 12:11:29', '2025-10-04 16:16:10'),
(93, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 32, 'Color: BLACK - Advanced Smartwatch With Three Bands And Wellness + Activity Tracker', 'color-black-advanced-smartwatch-with-three-bands-and-wellness-activity-tracker', 'local', 'K290-39484485075030', 'Color: BLACK - Advanced Smartwatch With Three Bands And Wellness + Activity Tracker', 'Color: BLACK - Advanced Smartwatch With Three Bands And Wellness + Activity Tracker', 'Color: BLACK - Advanced Smartwatch With Three Bands And Wellness + Activity Tracker', ' Latest advanced smartwatch with wellness and activity tracker.  Multi features that make your daily life fruitful with your personal well-being data available at every step on your wrist.   It offers three bands that are easily interchangeable to suit your present environment from everyday to casual to a more active sporty look all can be done with this smartwatch.  Customize the face of the watch to your desire or use hundreds of different custom backgrounds to fit your needs.  Works hand in hand with your phone to deliver messages and track your steps count your heartbeat pulse or show you your wellness data on the screen any time.  All up to date as your personal well wishes would do.  So many features are fitted in this smartwatch that when it is compared with many others and it will still be ranked on the top.  Everyday Wear - A bold solid band buckle style secure and ready for any activity.  Select dial and connect to your phone via Bluetooth and the Free APP and you are all set.  You can have a retro dial or digital dial or just about any dial you can think of.  Change it on the fly. Active Wear - A perforated stylish two-tone band with...', ' Latest advanced smartwatch with wellness and activity tracker.  Multi features that make your daily life fruitful with your personal well-being data available at every step on your wrist.   It offers three bands that are easily interchangeable to suit your present environment from everyday to casual to a more active sporty look all can be done with this smartwatch.  Customize the face of the watch to your desire or use hundreds of different custom backgrounds to fit your needs.  Works hand in hand with your phone to deliver messages and track your steps count your heartbeat pulse or show you your wellness data on the screen any time.  All up to date as your personal well wishes would do.  So many features are fitted in this smartwatch that when it is compared with many others and it will still be ranked on the top.  Everyday Wear - A bold solid band buckle style secure and ready for any activity.  Select dial and connect to your phone via Bluetooth and the Free APP and you are all set.  You can have a retro dial or digital dial or just about any dial you can think of.  Change it on the fly. Active Wear - A perforated stylish two-tone band with multiples vented holes for air circulation that keeps your wrist sweat-free during your sports and activity.  Secure buckle style belt. Casual Wear - A rustic fabric weaved band is waterproof and works well with a loosely worn watch like a bracelet on your wrist.  Get all your notifications without having to find a place on your dinner table for your smartphone.  Three Band combination is a unique package.  A smartwatch that you have been looking for which has it all.  Features:The size of the watch: 1.69 inch or 42mm Full Touch OLED Screen Works with Apple and Android Phones thru Free APP. Touch Screen Bluetooth Connectivity Incoming call Alert Weather Forecast Message Notification Social Media Connect IP67 Waterproof Standard Alarm Reminder Sedentary Reminder Calorie Burned counter Sleep Monitoring Heart Rate Monitoring Blood Pressure Monitoring estimated readingBlood Oxygen Monitoring. 8 Different sports activity tracking (Brisk Walking, Jogging, Cycling, Rope Jumping, Badminton, Basketball, Soccer, and Swimming) Works as a remote control for your phone to take pictures. Select your own watch background change anytime from 100\'s of built in. Large battery size 2 days of constant use with 20 days of standby power.Supports multiple languages like - English, Spanish, German, French, Chinese, Japanese, and Korean.  Just set up your language desired from the app. Choose from a selection of 8 colors of band which comes in 3 styles for each color selected  Recharge the watch in 3 hours or less with included charging cable that will connect to any USB port.LINK TO THE VIDEO: https://vimeo.com/675676977         ', 159.95, 64, '1759574770_68e0faf273b3b.jpg', NULL, '{\"Brand\":\"Motormax\",\"UPC\":\"723466579384\",\"Weight\":\"0.25\",\"Condition\":\"N\"}', 1, '2025-08-28 12:11:30', '2025-10-04 16:16:10'),
(95, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 32, 'Color: BLUE - PureTech Ultrasonic Fruits And Veggie Cleaner', 'color-blue-puretech-ultrasonic-fruits-and-veggie-cleaner', 'local', 'K290-39934788894806', 'Color: BLUE - PureTech Ultrasonic Fruits And Veggie Cleaner', 'Color: BLUE - PureTech Ultrasonic Fruits And Veggie Cleaner', 'Color: BLUE - PureTech Ultrasonic Fruits And Veggie Cleaner', 'Be totally in charge of your family\'s health and nutritional needs.When you make it a point to buy only organic produce as much as possible, you also need to know the fact that even organically grown produce is sprayed with some level of pesticide and herbicides to protect the crops from predators and diseases. It\'s always best to thoroughly wash and clean the residue of those pesticides and herbicides before cooking, or else they can enter our system and can be harmful to our health. Let the PureTech Ultrasonic Cleaner take over your kitchen essentials, just add it to plain water with your fruits and vegetables while you wash and clean them. Press on the switch, and it will faithfully start cleaning your fruits and veggies, without damaging them from the outside and without destroying the nutritional values from the inside. So simple and genius! You can also purify your tap water, and keep your small kitchen utensils, tableware, or even your fine jewelry germ-free by simply adding this Ultrasonic cleaner to the water.DETAILS:Such an easy way to preserve food for the longest time free of germs.Very convenient to carry anywhere outdoor for picnics and camping as it can fit...', 'Be totally in charge of your family\'s health and nutritional needs.When you make it a point to buy only organic produce as much as possible, you also need to know the fact that even organically grown produce is sprayed with some level of pesticide and herbicides to protect the crops from predators and diseases. It\'s always best to thoroughly wash and clean the residue of those pesticides and herbicides before cooking, or else they can enter our system and can be harmful to our health. Let the PureTech Ultrasonic Cleaner take over your kitchen essentials, just add it to plain water with your fruits and vegetables while you wash and clean them. Press on the switch, and it will faithfully start cleaning your fruits and veggies, without damaging them from the outside and without destroying the nutritional values from the inside. So simple and genius! You can also purify your tap water, and keep your small kitchen utensils, tableware, or even your fine jewelry germ-free by simply adding this Ultrasonic cleaner to the water.DETAILS:Such an easy way to preserve food for the longest time free of germs.Very convenient to carry anywhere outdoor for picnics and camping as it can fit the palm of your hand.Large-capacity 4400mah long-lasting battery.It is wireless and can be used for 25 + times with single charge.It is IPX7 waterproof. It comes in various colors to choose from.Get more for everyday use, each sold separately.', 179.95, 21, '1759574770_68e0faf2887e5.jpg', NULL, '{\"Brand\":\"Motormax\",\"UPC\":\"723466582728\",\"Weight\":\"0.00\",\"Condition\":\"N\"}', 1, '2025-08-28 12:11:30', '2025-10-04 16:16:10');
