 be done with this smartwatch. Customize the face of the watch to your desire or use hundreds of different custom backgrounds to fit your needs or make your own.Works hand in hand with your phone to deliver messages, track your steps, count your heartbeat, pulse show you your wellness data on the screen at any time, all up to date. So many features are fitted in this Smartwatch that when compared with many others, it will still be ranked at the top. DETAILS:Perfect for everyday Wear - A quick-wear magnetic band that you can throw on your wrist for an instant wrap, secure and ready for any activity. Select dial, connect to your phone via Bluetooth and the Free APP, and you are all set. You can have a retro dial or digital dial, or just about any dial you can think of. Change it on the fly.Casual Wear - A solid standard band with a waterproof buckle that works well with a loosely worn watch like a bracelet on your wrist.  Get notifications without finding a place on your dinner table for your Smartphone.   Bands are interchangeable and easily removable.  Any standard Smart Watch Band will fit a 42mm watch.SmartPRO is a Smartwatch you have been looking for that has it all. Features:The size of the watch: is 1.7 inches or 42mm.Full Touch OLED Screen in Rectangle or Round shape dials.Works with Apple and Android Phones thru a Free APP.Touch Screen.Bluetooth Connectivity.Incoming call Alert.Weather Forecast.Message Notification.Social Media Connect.IP67 Waterproof Standard.Alarm Reminder.Sedentary Reminder.Calorie Burned counter.Sleep Monitoring.Heart Rate Monitoring.Blood Pressure Monitoring.10 Different sports activity tracking (Brisk Walking, Jogging, Cycling, Rope Jumping, Badminton, Basketball, Soccer, Swimming, and more).It works as a remote control for your phone to take pictures.Select your watch background, and change it anytime from 100\'s built-in.Large battery size. 2 days of constant use with 20 days of standby power.Recharge the watch in 3 hours or less with an included charging cable connecting to any USB port.Choose from a selection of 8 colors of the magnetic band in 2 styles rectangle or round dials.What is in the box: 1 x Smart Watch, 1 x Bands, 1x Charging Cable, Manual + Free App on IOS and Android platform to install. ** This is not a medical device; all results shown are only for reference purposes.**  ', 150.00, 95, '1759574770_68e0faf2cbc1d.jpg', NULL, '{\"Brand\":\"Motormax\",\"UPC\":\"723466583138\",\"Weight\":\"0.33\",\"Condition\":\"N\"}', 1, '2025-08-28 12:11:30', '2025-10-04 16:16:10'),
(97, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 32, 'Color: Pink Stone,Size: 10 - LUMINA Pure & Pink Banquet Rings', 'color-pink-stonesize-10-lumina-pure-pink-banquet-rings', 'local', 'K290-6053909125', 'Color: Pink Stone,Size: 10 - LUMINA Pure & Pink Banquet Rings', 'Color: Pink Stone,Size: 10 - LUMINA Pure & Pink Banquet Rings', 'Color: Pink Stone,Size: 10 - LUMINA Pure & Pink Banquet Rings', 'Shining as heavenly as the brightest stars and as lustrous as the chandeliers The LUMINA Rings are as sumptuous and elaborated as the banquet dinner you want to attend. Choose one for the occasion and let your face glow in the reflection of your Luminous Ring!Look your stylish self with LUMINA without even trying too hard just slip it on along with your evening dress and you will get compliments while you hold onto your glass of champagne and enjoy feast of desserts.Give the evening the sheen and radiance it rightly deserves with LUMINA. Pure, Pink or both. DETAILS:Three inseparable Diamond Crystal Bands come together to form Lumina Ring Platinum Plated for highest and lasting luster.Meant for special occasions.Center Stones are Princess Cut channel Set outside circle stones are round cut prong set.  All hand set with AAA quality Crystal almost 12 cts total weight.It comes in sizes 6, 7, 8, 9,10, and 11It comes in Sweet Pink Diamond Crystals and Pure Crystal Clear Diamonds. Each sold separately.It comes in a Gift Box for safekeeping and gift giving.', 'Shining as heavenly as the brightest stars and as lustrous as the chandeliers The LUMINA Rings are as sumptuous and elaborated as the banquet dinner you want to attend. Choose one for the occasion and let your face glow in the reflection of your Luminous Ring!Look your stylish self with LUMINA without even trying too hard just slip it on along with your evening dress and you will get compliments while you hold onto your glass of champagne and enjoy feast of desserts.Give the evening the sheen and radiance it rightly deserves with LUMINA. Pure, Pink or both. DETAILS:Three inseparable Diamond Crystal Bands come together to form Lumina Ring Platinum Plated for highest and lasting luster.Meant for special occasions.Center Stones are Princess Cut channel Set outside circle stones are round cut prong set.  All hand set with AAA quality Crystal almost 12 cts total weight.It comes in sizes 6, 7, 8, 9,10, and 11It comes in Sweet Pink Diamond Crystals and Pure Crystal Clear Diamonds. Each sold separately.It comes in a Gift Box for safekeeping and gift giving.', 79.95, 47, '1759574771_68e0faf315f6f.jpg', NULL, '{\"Brand\":\"Motormax\",\"UPC\":\"740016258681\",\"Weight\":\"0.00\",\"Condition\":\"N\"}', 1, '2025-08-28 12:11:31', '2025-10-04 16:16:11'),
(98, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 32, 'Size: 10 - Love Struck Diamond Crystals Platinum Plated Halo Ring', 'size-10-love-struck-diamond-crystals-platinum-plated-halo-ring', 'local', 'K290-7020706949', 'Size: 10 - Love Struck Diamond Crystals Platinum Plated Halo Ring', 'Size: 10 - Love Struck Diamond Crystals Platinum Plated Halo Ring', 'Size: 10 - Love Struck Diamond Crystals Platinum Plated Halo Ring', 'Get Love Struck!This time around by the Diamond Crystal Platinum Halo Ring and you know your sweet proposal does not have to wait any longer. You often had dreams of a spectacular Ring for your sweetheart to propose with tell her you have finally discovered it but just cannot define it\'s beauty and she needs to see it to believe it.The Diamond Crystal is breathtaking on its own, it\'s clarity speaks of your affection for her and the Pave band will look like a Big smile on her finger. Let her be as Love Struck as you are! This Ring for sure is going to make her heart melt and she is going to say Yes!Details:The Modern and Traditional Diamond Crystal with Halo Measures 12mm center stone of 5ct wt., surrounded by 2mm stones all round in shape.The Crystal split shank Band is an Alloy metal with Platinum plating assures long lasting shine and makes it a unique choice.It comes in Sizes: 6, 7, 8, 9,10 .It comes in a Gift Box for Gift Giving and Safe Keeping.1 Year Warranty on workmanship and polish.', 'Get Love Struck!This time around by the Diamond Crystal Platinum Halo Ring and you know your sweet proposal does not have to wait any longer. You often had dreams of a spectacular Ring for your sweetheart to propose with tell her you have finally discovered it but just cannot define it\'s beauty and she needs to see it to believe it.The Diamond Crystal is breathtaking on its own, it\'s clarity speaks of your affection for her and the Pave band will look like a Big smile on her finger. Let her be as Love Struck as you are! This Ring for sure is going to make her heart melt and she is going to say Yes!Details:The Modern and Traditional Diamond Crystal with Halo Measures 12mm center stone of 5ct wt., surrounded by 2mm stones all round in shape.The Crystal split shank Band is an Alloy metal with Platinum plating assures long lasting shine and makes it a unique choice.It comes in Sizes: 6, 7, 8, 9,10 .It comes in a Gift Box for Gift Giving and Safe Keeping.1 Year Warranty on workmanship and polish.', 74.95, 46, '1759574771_68e0faf3611b1.jpg', NULL, '{\"Brand\":\"Motormax\",\"UPC\":\"740016242031\",\"Weight\":\"0.03\",\"Condition\":\"N\"}', 1, '2025-08-28 12:11:31', '2025-10-04 16:16:11'),
(99, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 32, 'Original Apple iPad Air 10.5-inch (  A12 Chip TouchID Super Portable IOS Tablet Deep Gray 256GB', 'original-apple-ipad-air-105-inch-a12-chip-touchid-super-portable-ios-tablet-deep-gray-256gb', 'local', 'K484-PCO_007MQWWJ', 'Original Apple iPad Air 10.5-inch (  A12 Chip TouchID Super Portable IOS Tablet Deep Gray 256GB', 'Original Apple iPad Air 10.5-inch (  A12 Chip TouchID Super Portable IOS Tablet Deep Gray 256GB', 'Original Apple iPad Air 10.5-inch (  A12 Chip TouchID Super Portable IOS Tablet Deep Gray 256GB', '<p>The new iPad Air 2019; technology, beauty and power in one slim body. From every angle, it is so beautiful, fashionable, full of technology.</p><p>The A12 Bionic chip with Neural Engine enables a remarkable level of power and intelligence.</p><p>A 4-core graphics engine in the A12 Bionic chip delivers amazing performance for incredible augmented reality experiences.</p><p>The immersive 10.5‑inch Retina display with wide color lets you see photos, videos, and games in vivid, true‑to life detail.</p><p>True Tone dynamically adjusts white balance based on the light around you.</p><p>6.1mm, 458g, It\'s thin and light, and has advanced wireless connectivity. And with up to 10 hours of battery life.</p><p>Description:</p><p>Model:ipad air</p><p>Brand: APPLE</p><p>Model: iPad Air</p><p>Configuration: WLAN + A12 chip / Retina screen</p><p>Screen size: 10.5-Inch</p><p>Year: 2019</p><p>Machine weight: 0.47kg</p><p>Item Type: Tablet PC</p><p>Supporting Language: Multi</p><p>Network: Wifi</p><p>Display resolution: 2224x1668</p><p>Touch Screen Type: Capacitive Screen</p><p>Memory Capacity: 3GB</p><p>Feature: Ultra Slim</p><p>Feature: Fingerprint Recognition</p><p>Display Size: 10.5 \'</p><p>Operating System: ios</p><p>Processor Core: Octa Core</p><p>Extend Port: Earphone Jack</p><p>Extend Port: Lightning</p><p>Cell Capacity: 10 Hours Capacity</p><p>Package: Yes</p><p>Net Weight: 456</p><p>Camera: Second Webcam</p><p>Second Webcam Pixels: 8MP</p><p>Google Play: No</p><p>Item Condition: New</p><p>Panel Type: IPS</p><p>Brand Name: APPLE</p><p>Package including:</p><p>1*ipad air(as shown)</p><p>Note: Light shooting and different displays may cause the color of the item in the picture a little different from the real thing. The measurement allowed error is...', '<p>The new iPad Air 2019; technology, beauty and power in one slim body. From every angle, it is so beautiful, fashionable, full of technology.</p><p>The A12 Bionic chip with Neural Engine enables a remarkable level of power and intelligence.</p><p>A 4-core graphics engine in the A12 Bionic chip delivers amazing performance for incredible augmented reality experiences.</p><p>The immersive 10.5‑inch Retina display with wide color lets you see photos, videos, and games in vivid, true‑to life detail.</p><p>True Tone dynamically adjusts white balance based on the light around you.</p><p>6.1mm, 458g, It\'s thin and light, and has advanced wireless connectivity. And with up to 10 hours of battery life.</p><p>Description:</p><p>Model:ipad air</p><p>Brand: APPLE</p><p>Model: iPad Air</p><p>Configuration: WLAN + A12 chip / Retina screen</p><p>Screen size: 10.5-Inch</p><p>Year: 2019</p><p>Machine weight: 0.47kg</p><p>Item Type: Tablet PC</p><p>Supporting Language: Multi</p><p>Network: Wifi</p><p>Display resolution: 2224x1668</p><p>Touch Screen Type: Capacitive Screen</p><p>Memory Capacity: 3GB</p><p>Feature: Ultra Slim</p><p>Feature: Fingerprint Recognition</p><p>Display Size: 10.5 \'</p><p>Operating System: ios</p><p>Processor Core: Octa Core</p><p>Extend Port: Earphone Jack</p><p>Extend Port: Lightning</p><p>Cell Capacity: 10 Hours Capacity</p><p>Package: Yes</p><p>Net Weight: 456</p><p>Camera: Second Webcam</p><p>Second Webcam Pixels: 8MP</p><p>Google Play: No</p><p>Item Condition: New</p><p>Panel Type: IPS</p><p>Brand Name: APPLE</p><p>Package including:</p><p>1*ipad air(as shown)</p><p>Note: Light shooting and different displays may cause the color of the item in the picture a little different from the real thing. The measurement allowed error is +/- 1-3cm.</p><br><div class=\"panel panel-info\"><div class=\"panel-heading\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">IMPORT: THIS ITEM IS SHIPPED FROM CHINA. PLEASE EXPECT UP TO 25 DAYS FOR DELIVERY</div></div>', 1350.29, 10, '1759574771_68e0faf386a9e.jpg', NULL, '{\"Brand\":\"Motormax\",\"UPC\":\"740016242031\",\"Weight\":\"1.99\",\"Condition\":\"N\"}', 1, '2025-08-28 12:11:31', '2025-10-04 16:16:11'),
(100, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 32, '2.4GHz Wireless Mouse Blue', '24ghz-wireless-mouse-blue', 'local', 'P595-IMOUSES50L', '2.4GHz Wireless Mouse Blue', '2.4GHz Wireless Mouse Blue', '2.4GHz Wireless Mouse Blue', 'Adesso 2.4GHz Wireless Ergonomic Mini Mouse -  iMouse S50 M325 - Blue, Experience new levels of productivity with the Adesso iMouse S50 2.4GHz Wireless Mini Ergonomic Mouse. This advanced wireless mouse offers you 30 feet of wireless freedom and eliminates the constraints wired mice often cause. Its optical sensor tracking method lets you work on any surface with better speed and accuracy. In addition, the mouse includes a built-in DPI resolution of 1200 for precise navigating and fast maneuvering. All these features, including it?s portable, compact mini size, provide excellent control, minimal hand movement and a mouse you can take or travel with anywhere.', 'Adesso 2.4GHz Wireless Ergonomic Mini Mouse -  iMouse S50 M325 - Blue, Experience new levels of productivity with the Adesso iMouse S50 2.4GHz Wireless Mini Ergonomic Mouse. This advanced wireless mouse offers you 30 feet of wireless freedom and eliminates the constraints wired mice often cause. Its optical sensor tracking method lets you work on any surface with better speed and accuracy. In addition, the mouse includes a built-in DPI resolution of 1200 for precise navigating and fast maneuvering. All these features, including it?s portable, compact mini size, provide excellent control, minimal hand movement and a mouse you can take or travel with anywhere.', 18.59, 2, '1759574772_68e0faf438d23.jpg', 2, '{\"Brand\":\"Adesso Inc.\",\"UPC\":\"783750008877\",\"Weight\":\"0.25\",\"Condition\":\"N\"}', 1, '2025-08-28 12:11:36', '2026-01-22 17:19:30'),
(101, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 32, 'IDEAL 62-200 LinkMaster RJ45 CAT5E/6 Ethernet Wiremapper Tester', 'ideal-62-200-linkmaster-rj45-cat5e6-ethernet-wiremapper-tester', 'local', 'R810-IDI62200', 'IDEAL 62-200 LinkMaster RJ45 CAT5E/6 Ethernet Wiremapper Tester', 'IDEAL 62-200 LinkMaster RJ45 CAT5E/6 Ethernet Wiremapper Tester', 'IDEAL 62-200 LinkMaster RJ45 CAT5E/6 Ethernet Wiremapper Tester', '• LED-based basic wiremapper verifies cable continuity;• Identifies errors by pair--shorts, opens, miswires, reversals, and split pairs;• Tests for shield continuity;• Designed for CAT 3/5/5E/6/6A cables;• RJ45 interface for 8-conductor twisted pair cables;• Debug feature cycles through errors one at a time;• LED green/red lights helps pass/fail visibility in darker locations;• Includes main unit and remote for 1-person testing;<br /><br />Length: 10.25\"<br />Width: 5.15\"<br />Height: 1.80\"', '• LED-based basic wiremapper verifies cable continuity;• Identifies errors by pair--shorts, opens, miswires, reversals, and split pairs;• Tests for shield continuity;• Designed for CAT 3/5/5E/6/6A cables;• RJ45 interface for 8-conductor twisted pair cables;• Debug feature cycles through errors one at a time;• LED green/red lights helps pass/fail visibility in darker locations;• Includes main unit and remote for 1-person testing;<br /><br />Length: 10.25\"<br />Width: 5.15\"<br />Height: 1.80\"', 38.99, 7, '1759574772_68e0faf46f75a.jpg', NULL, '{\"Brand\":\"IDEAL(R)\",\"UPC\":\"783250622009\",\"Weight\":\"0.68\",\"Condition\":\"N\"}', 1, '2025-08-28 12:11:36', '2025-10-04 16:16:13'),
