igh 10000:1 contrast ratio allows the projector for more realistic color reproduction and highlights darker details, tiny details can be captured on the big screen, bring you a shocking, immersive viewing experience.</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">[300\" Giant Screen & 50% ZOOM Function] The portable projector offers a 32\"- 300 \" projection size with a projection distance between 3.6ft-32.8ft, allows you get the best viewing effect in your home theater(Including the 100\'\' projector screen, even outdoors we can easily enjoy an movie feast). With 50% zoom function, you can reduce the image size from 100% to 50% without moving the home projector. It can also supports front, rear and ceiling installation, you can install as you need.</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">[Compatible with Multi Devices] The Bluetooth projector provides HDMI/2*USB/AV port/3.5mm audio port, which can connect with TV stick, Smartphone, Laptop, Chromecast, DVD Player, external speakers, PS4, USB flash, etc. Easily meet your movie, match, and game needs.(Due to copyright issues, it can\'t support watching the videos on Netflix, Prime Video, Hulu, Disney etc while screen mirroring, but it will works well by HDMI connection if you use the TV Stick or Roku Express.)</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">[Built-in HiFi Stereo Speakers & Detachable Dust Filter] This outdoor projector equipped with HiFi stereo speakers, it provides you with original audio fidelity, restores every detailed sound effect, and allows you to enjoy the ultimate auditory feast! With a detachable dust filter, the projector can prevents dust entering the machine or falling on the lens, reducing fan blockage and light bulbs being dusted and extending the using life.</span></li></ul><ul><li class=\"postpurchase-included-components-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #0f1111; font-family: \'Amazon Ember\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Projector</span></li><li class=\"postpurchase-included-components-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #0f1111; font-family: \'Amazon Ember\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">100 Inches Projector Screen</span></li><li class=\"postpurchase-included-components-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #0f1111; font-family: \'Amazon Ember\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Remote Control</span></li><li class=\"postpurchase-included-components-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #0f1111; font-family: \'Amazon Ember\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">HDMI Cable/AC Power Cable/AV Cable</span></li><li class=\"postpurchase-included-components-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: #0f1111; font-family: \'Amazon Ember\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">User Manual</span></li></ul>', 145.65, 500, '1759574774_68e0faf606fd2.jpg', NULL, '{\"Brand\":\"TAYLOR(R) PRECISION PRODUCTS\",\"UPC\":\"082197104075\",\"Weight\":\"66.99\",\"Condition\":\"N\"}', 1, '2025-08-28 12:11:42', '2025-10-04 16:16:14'),
(103, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 32, 'EOL One Love Massage Candle F-M', 'eol-one-love-massage-candle-f-m', 'local', 'A451-A02861', 'EOL One Love Massage Candle F-M', 'EOL One Love Massage Candle F-M', 'EOL One Love Massage Candle F-M', 'Eye of Love Pheromone Massage Candle is made with a shea butter base and other natural ingredients. It melts completely into a high quality oil that can be used for a massage or as your daily moisturizer. Includes free One Love Pheromone Parfum Sample.<br><br>The fragrance features a sweet blend of citrusy rose feminine lily and sensual jasmine. The aroma of musky vanilla will caress his senses and keep him under your spell. Specially formulated for special occasions to increase the love romance and desire with your partner.<br><ul><li>Melts into a warm oil that won\'t burn your skin</li><li>Contains fragrance pheromones & moisturizers</li><li>Soft floral fragrance</li></ul><br>USE: Light candle and let burn until starts melting (approx. 20 min) Use as your daily moisturizer or for a sensual massage.', 'Eye of Love Pheromone Massage Candle is made with a shea butter base and other natural ingredients. It melts completely into a high quality oil that can be used for a massage or as your daily moisturizer. Includes free One Love Pheromone Parfum Sample.<br><br>The fragrance features a sweet blend of citrusy rose feminine lily and sensual jasmine. The aroma of musky vanilla will caress his senses and keep him under your spell. Specially formulated for special occasions to increase the love romance and desire with your partner.<br><ul><li>Melts into a warm oil that won\'t burn your skin</li><li>Contains fragrance pheromones & moisturizers</li><li>Soft floral fragrance</li></ul><br>USE: Light candle and let burn until starts melting (approx. 20 min) Use as your daily moisturizer or for a sensual massage.', 26.30, 30, '1759574725_68e0fac533179.jpg', NULL, '{\"Brand\":\"A&R Naturelles Inc Eye of Love\",\"UPC\":\"818141011065\",\"Weight\":\"0.85\",\"Condition\":\"N\"}', 1, '2025-08-28 14:30:34', '2025-10-04 16:15:26'),
(104, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 32, 'Wheeled Flight Case Black 22.8\"x17.7\"x10.6\" PP', 'wheeled-flight-case-black-228x177x106-pp', 'local', 'A949-51797', 'Wheeled Flight Case Black 22.8\"x17.7\"x10.6\" PP', 'Wheeled Flight Case Black 22.8\"x17.7\"x10.6\" PP', 'Wheeled Flight Case Black 22.8\"x17.7\"x10.6\" PP', 'Size: 58 x 45 x 27 cm<br><p>This handy flight case is a perfect combination of heavy-duty protection and easy transportation. It is ideal for travelling with your valuable items.</p><p> </p><ul><li>Multiple protection: A tough outer shell allows shock resistance, while a strong seal creates water protection. The lockable function of the road case also adds extra safety.</li><li>Portable design: Practical wheels and a retractable pull handle allow you to take the hard case more conveniently.</li><li>Soft foam insert: The transport case comes with removable foam inserts to store your belongings snugly and safely.</li><li>Pressure valve: The pressure valve can maintain the balance between internal and external pressures to help the toolbox adjust better at different elevation levels.</li><li>Durable material: The flight case with foam is made of polypropylene and ABS, which makes it temperature proof. So, it offers a long service life.</li></ul> <ul><li>Color: Black</li><li>Case material: Polypropylene, ABS</li><li>Foam material: Polyurethane</li><li>Overall dimensions: 22.8\" x 17.7\" x 10.6\" (L x W x H)</li><li>Inner dimensions: 20.5\" x 15.4\" x 7.5\" (L x W x H)</li><li>Height of handle (extended): 38.2\"</li><li class=\"legalDocument\">California Proposition 65<br/><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"></span></p></li></ul>', 'Size: 58 x 45 x 27 cm<br><p>This handy flight case is a perfect combination of heavy-duty protection and easy transportation. It is ideal for travelling with your valuable items.</p><p> </p><ul><li>Multiple protection: A tough outer shell allows shock resistance, while a strong seal creates water protection. The lockable function of the road case also adds extra safety.</li><li>Portable design: Practical wheels and a retractable pull handle allow you to take the hard case more conveniently.</li><li>Soft foam insert: The transport case comes with removable foam inserts to store your belongings snugly and safely.</li><li>Pressure valve: The pressure valve can maintain the balance between internal and external pressures to help the toolbox adjust better at different elevation levels.</li><li>Durable material: The flight case with foam is made of polypropylene and ABS, which makes it temperature proof. So, it offers a long service life.</li></ul> <ul><li>Color: Black</li><li>Case material: Polypropylene, ABS</li><li>Foam material: Polyurethane</li><li>Overall dimensions: 22.8\" x 17.7\" x 10.6\" (L x W x H)</li><li>Inner dimensions: 20.5\" x 15.4\" x 7.5\" (L x W x H)</li><li>Height of handle (extended): 38.2\"</li><li class=\"legalDocument\">California Proposition 65<br/><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"></span></p></li></ul>', 191.15, 14, '1759574726_68e0fac655b90.jpg', NULL, '{\"Brand\":\"A&R Naturelles Inc Eye of Love\",\"UPC\":\"8720845724467\",\"Weight\":\"20.26\",\"Condition\":\"N\"}', 1, '2025-08-28 14:30:34', '2025-10-04 16:15:26'),
(105, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 32, 'Desk White Engineered Wood 78.7 in long Rotatable Desk', 'desk-white-engineered-wood-787-in-long-rotatable-desk', 'local', 'A949-801103', 'Desk White Engineered Wood 78.7 in long Rotatable Desk', 'Desk White Engineered Wood 78.7 in long Rotatable Desk', 'Desk White Engineered Wood 78.7 in long Rotatable Desk', 'Size: 78.7 in long,19.7 in wide<br><p>This corner desk combines style with practicality, making it a fabulous choice for home or office. With generous sizes at 78.7 in long and 19.7 in wide, it offers loads of workspace and boosts the decor of your study, living room, or bedroom.</p> <ul><li><strong>Modern Design:</strong> The sleek and minimalist look of this corner desk makes it a stylish addition to any room, fitting seamlessly into offices, living spaces, or studies. The smooth surfaces in a chic white and Sonoma oak color combination create a stylish contrast and add warmth to the overall environment.</li><li><strong>Rotatable Surface:</strong> Thanks to its innovative rotatable design, this desk allows you to easily adjust the angle, making it perfect for various activities like writing or working on a computer.</li><li><strong>Ample Storage:</strong> With a large working area, this desk provides significant surface space to keep everything organized and easily reachable, whether you\'re working professionally or studying.</li><li><strong>Sturdy Construction:</strong> Built from durable engineered wood, it\'s crafted to resist daily use, ensuring reliable support for all your equipment.</li><li><strong>Versatile Use:</strong> This desk\'s stylish design lets it shine in different settings-working as a writing table, office workstation, or an entryway console.</li></ul> <ul><li>Color: White</li><li>Shape: Rectangular</li><li>Material: Engineered Wood</li><li>Indoor/Outdoor: Indoor Only</li><li>Cover Included:...', 'Size: 78.7 in long,19.7 in wide<br><p>This corner desk combines style with practicality, making it a fabulous choice for home or office. With generous sizes at 78.7 in long and 19.7 in wide, it offers loads of workspace and boosts the decor of your study, living room, or bedroom.</p> <ul><li><strong>Modern Design:</strong> The sleek and minimalist look of this corner desk makes it a stylish addition to any room, fitting seamlessly into offices, living spaces, or studies. The smooth surfaces in a chic white and Sonoma oak color combination create a stylish contrast and add warmth to the overall environment.</li><li><strong>Rotatable Surface:</strong> Thanks to its innovative rotatable design, this desk allows you to easily adjust the angle, making it perfect for various activities like writing or working on a computer.</li><li><strong>Ample Storage:</strong> With a large working area, this desk provides significant surface space to keep everything organized and easily reachable, whether you\'re working professionally or studying.</li><li><strong>Sturdy Construction:</strong> Built from durable engineered wood, it\'s crafted to resist daily use, ensuring reliable support for all your equipment.</li><li><strong>Versatile Use:</strong> This desk\'s stylish design lets it shine in different settings-working as a writing table, office workstation, or an entryway console.</li></ul> <ul><li>Color: White</li><li>Shape: Rectangular</li><li>Material: Engineered Wood</li><li>Indoor/Outdoor: Indoor Only</li><li>Cover Included: No</li><li>Room: Office</li><li>Maximum Number of People: 1</li><li>Mounting Included: No</li><li>Dimensions: 19.7 x 78.7 x 29.9 in (W x L x H)</li><li>Min-Max Dimensions: 78.7 in max / 47.2 in min</li><li>Weight: 67.24 lbs</li><li>Delivery Contains: Desk components, assembly manual</li><li>Assembly Required: Yes</li><li>Recommended Number of People for Assembly: 1</li></ul>', 132.45, 13, '1759574728_68e0fac85fdcc.jpg', NULL, '{\"Brand\":\"A&R Naturelles Inc Eye of Love\",\"UPC\":\"8719883816890\",\"Weight\":\"67.24\",\"Condition\":\"N\"}', 1, '2025-08-28 14:3