ded seat with powerful vibration function<br />● With infrared heat of 104-131F for good blood circulation<br />● 3-level timer ensures auto shut off to save energy<br />● Thai shiatsu and rolling massage are useful to relieve fatigue<br />● Adjustable widths of 3\"-5.5\" for different people<br />● Remote control makes it easy to change the massage mode<br />● Detachable neck pillow and back flap for flexible use<br />● Side storage pocket keeps the remote control within reach<br />● Sweat-proof surface is convenient to clean<br />● Applicable to office chairs  leisure chairs  sofas  etc<br />● Comes with the UL certification for high security</p>', 264.00, 4, '1759574737_68e0fad168a33.jpg', NULL, '{\"Brand\":\"FAXYSON\",\"UPC\":\"6473511163962\",\"Weight\":\"1.00\",\"Condition\":\"N\"}', 1, '2025-08-28 14:30:44', '2025-10-04 16:15:37'),
