 16000   Battery 6V/4.5AH   Charger Input 100-120V/60Hz   Charger Output 6V/1.0A   Charging Time 8-12 Hours  Box Qty 1(May vary by batch)<br /><p>● Premium motor and battery for outstanding performance<br />● Bright LED headlight for a cool and fun experience<br />● Built-in music  story and FM modes for extra fun<br />● Anti-slip handlebars and comfortable seat for coziness<br />● Removable training wheels for more exciting riding<br />● One-button start and go forward or backward<br />● Slow start function avoids frightening kids accidentally<br />● Realistic throttle pedal for immersive riding<br />● Threaded tires go well on different types of road<br />● Integrated charging hole for great convenience<br />● Simulated exhaust pipes for more authentic appearance<br />● ASTM and CPSIA certifications for enhanced reliability</p>  ', 395.00, 149, '1759574739_68e0fad31e5bd.jpg', NULL, '{\"Brand\":\"FAXYSON\",\"UPC\":\"197867568436\",\"Weight\":\"1.00\",\"Condition\":\"N\"}', 1, '2025-08-28 14:30:47', '2025-10-04 16:15:39'),
(112, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 32, 'Brentwood Full Size Stem / Spray / Dry Iron', 'brentwood-full-size-stem-spray-dry-iron', 'local', 'D970-MPI-62', 'Brentwood Full Size Stem / Spray / Dry Iron', 'Brentwood Full Size Stem / Spray / Dry Iron', 'Brentwood Full Size Stem / Spray / Dry Iron', 'The powerful 1200w Brentwood Non-Stick Steam Iron quickly and efficiently eliminates wrinkles giving your clothes a crisp, polished look. Features fabric selection guide, dry, steam and spray settings and water level window. Use the vertical steam setting to remove wrinkles from curtains, drapes, linens and more. Our stylish jet black steam iron accents the decor of every home.<br>WARNING: This product can expose you to chemicals including DEHP, which is known to the State of California to cause cancer and/or reproductive harm. For more information, go to www.P65Warnings.ca.gov.', 'The powerful 1200w Brentwood Non-Stick Steam Iron quickly and efficiently eliminates wrinkles giving your clothes a crisp, polished look. Features fabric selection guide, dry, steam and spray settings and water level window. Use the vertical steam setting to remove wrinkles from curtains, drapes, linens and more. Our stylish jet black steam iron accents the decor of every home.<br>WARNING: This product can expose you to chemicals including DEHP, which is known to the State of California to cause cancer and/or reproductive harm. For more information, go to www.P65Warnings.ca.gov.', 42.99, 21, '1759574741_68e0fad5af548.jpg', NULL, '{\"Brand\":\"BRENTWOOD\",\"UPC\":\"181225800627\",\"Weight\":\"5.00\",\"Condition\":\"N\"}', 1, '2025-08-28 14:30:51', '2025-10-04 16:15:41');
