(128, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 32, 'United States M142 High Mobility Artillery Rocket System (HIMARS) Desert Camo \"NEO Dragon Armor\" Series 1/72 Plastic Model by Dragon Models', 'united-states-m142-high-mobility-artillery-rocket-system-himars-desert-camo-neo-dragon-armor-series-172-plastic-model-by-dragon-models', 'local', 'F977-63018', 'United States M142 High Mobility Artillery Rocket System (HIMARS) Desert Camo \"NEO Dragon Armor\" Series 1/72 Plastic Model by Dragon Models', 'United States M142 High Mobility Artillery Rocket System (HIMARS) Desert Camo \"NEO Dragon Armor\" Series 1/72 Plastic Model by Dragon Models', 'United States M142 High Mobility Artillery Rocket System (HIMARS) Desert Camo \"NEO Dragon Armor\" Series 1/72 Plastic Model by Dragon Models', '<ul><li>Brand new 1/72 scale plastic model of United States M142 High Mobility Artillery Rocket System (HIMARS) Desert Camo \"NEO Dragon Armor\" Series plastic model by Dragon Models.</li><li>Limited edition.</li><li>Brand new box.</li><li>Detailed exterior.</li><li>Real rubber tires.</li><li>True-to-scale detail.</li><li><strong>Comes in plastic display showcase.</strong></li><li>This model does not have any openings.</li><li>Manufacturer\'s original unopened packaging.</li><li>Rocket system tilts for displaying in launch mode.</li><li>Dimensions approximately L-4.25, W-1.625, H-1.75 inches.</li><li>Pad printed markings and placards that won\'t fade or peel like decals for long-lasting.</li><li>High-quality markings include a protective display case to keep the model in pristine condition.</li><li>It is a highly detailed and accurate model, perfect for collectors and enthusiasts of military history.</li><li><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">HISTORY ASPECTS:</span><br />The U.S. M142 High Mobility Artillery Rocket System (HIMARS) in Desert Camo represents a formidable piece of artillery that has played a crucial role in modern military operations. Introduced in the early 2000s, the HIMARS provides the U.S. military with rapid and precise long-range strike capabilities. Its deployment in various conflicts has showcased its versatility and effectiveness on the battlefield.<br />One notable conflict where the HIMARS has proven its worth is in the wars in Iraq and Afghanistan. Its ability to launch a variety of munitions, including guided rockets and missiles, has allowed it to engage both...', '<ul><li>Brand new 1/72 scale plastic model of United States M142 High Mobility Artillery Rocket System (HIMARS) Desert Camo \"NEO Dragon Armor\" Series plastic model by Dragon Models.</li><li>Limited edition.</li><li>Brand new box.</li><li>Detailed exterior.</li><li>Real rubber tires.</li><li>True-to-scale detail.</li><li><strong>Comes in plastic display showcase.</strong></li><li>This model does not have any openings.</li><li>Manufacturer\'s original unopened packaging.</li><li>Rocket system tilts for displaying in launch mode.</li><li>Dimensions approximately L-4.25, W-1.625, H-1.75 inches.</li><li>Pad printed markings and placards that won\'t fade or peel like decals for long-lasting.</li><li>High-quality markings include a protective display case to keep the model in pristine condition.</li><li>It is a highly detailed and accurate model, perfect for collectors and enthusiasts of military history.</li><li><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">HISTORY ASPECTS:</span><br />The U.S. M142 High Mobility Artillery Rocket System (HIMARS) in Desert Camo represents a formidable piece of artillery that has played a crucial role in modern military operations. Introduced in the early 2000s, the HIMARS provides the U.S. military with rapid and precise long-range strike capabilities. Its deployment in various conflicts has showcased its versatility and effectiveness on the battlefield.<br />One notable conflict where the HIMARS has proven its worth is in the wars in Iraq and Afghanistan. Its ability to launch a variety of munitions, including guided rockets and missiles, has allowed it to engage both conventional and asymmetric threats. The Desert Camo variant, designed to blend into arid environments, became a familiar sight in the harsh landscapes of these regions. The HIMARS has demonstrated its importance in providing responsive and accurate fire support for ground forces, contributing significantly to the success of military operations.<br />Now, enthusiasts and collectors can own a piece of military history with the 1:72 scale model. This replica captures the essence of this powerful artillery system, making it a perfect addition to any military model collection. Whether you have a passion for military technology or an appreciation for the historical significance of modern artillery, the HIMARS scale model is a remarkable representation of precision and firepower.</li></ul><p> </p>', 76.60, 0, '1759574724_68e0fac42059a.jpg', NULL, '{\"Brand\":\"Dragon Models\",\"UPC\":\"089195630186\",\"Weight\":\"2.00\",\"Condition\":\"N\"}', 1, '2025-08-28 14:31:14', '2025-10-04 16:15:24'),
