(399, '6943f782ff9b61f73389caa0', 'https://autods-scraper-images.s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/b8f0636bf10db4264381c0e0561ce1d7.png', '4768370', NULL, 33, 'Kids Watch Fitness Tracker, Fitness Watches for Kids, Activity Tracker with Pedometers, Stopwatch, IP68 Waterproof, 11 Sport Modes Smart Watch for Kids Age 6-16 Years Old', 'kids-watch-fitness-tracker-fitness-watches-for-kids-activity-tracker-with-pedometers-stopwatch-ip68-waterproof-11-sport-modes-smart-watch-for-kids-age-6-16-years-old-6410ae', 'new', '3f4b9d6a-28c2-4b7f-a619-f2ee2d540d49', 'Kids Watch Fitness Tracker, Fitness Watches for Kids, Activity Tracker with Pedometers, Stopwatch, IP68 Waterproof, 11 Sport Modes Smart Watch for Kids Age 6-16 Years Old', NULL, '🎁【MULTIFUNCTIONAL FITNESS TRACKER】Multifunctional fitness tracker smartwatch with the function of Pedometer, Stopwatch, Alarm clock, time display, Calories c...', '🎁【MULTIFUNCTIONAL FITNESS TRACKER】Multifunctional fitness tracker smartwatch with the function of Pedometer, Stopwatch, Alarm clock, time display, Calories calculation etc.,11 Sport modes...', '<ul><li>🎁【MULTIFUNCTIONAL FITNESS TRACKER】Multifunctional fitness tracker smartwatch with the function of Pedometer, Stopwatch, Alarm clock, time display, Calories calculation etc.,11 Sport modes, such as Walking, Running, Cycling, Swimming, etc., Sedentary reminder, Drink water reminder, Call /SMS /Message reminder, etc., IP72 waterproof, It has GPS function, connects with your smartphone GPS, it can show you the movement tracker.</li><li>🎁【HEARTHY TRACKER】The fitness tracker can automatically monitor your daily real-time heartbeat, and track how well you sleep at night. Get the data about your sleeping trends via the app could help you adjust your habits and help you live healthier. The vibrating alarm clock can wake up you without disturbing others. All health data could be uploaded to the phone app \"H-band\".</li><li>🎁【FRIENDLY REMINDER】Our Fitness smartwatch will make life easier and smarter. The vibration alarm clock will wake up you without disturbing other people. When you connect this fitness tracker to your phone, you will never miss your calls/messages. You can set friendly reminders, such as walk after sitting for a long time, drinking water, and taking medicine, and with our fitness tracker, you will never forget the little but important daily things!</li><li>🎁【IP68 WATERPROOF】 IP68 waterproof makes this fitness tracker available to be worn while swimming, diving, or taking a shower. It only needs to be taken off before a hot bath. Come with a replaceable wristband, make it possible to change the looking, Our fitness tracker will accompany you in every joyful time. Great birthday gifts/ holiday gifts for kids. suit to kids age 6-24 years old.</li><li>🎁【COMPATIBILITY】Our smart watches could support iOS 8.0 or above, Android 4.4 or higher. Download the \"H Band\" app. 5 different wallpapers can be set. 2 kinds of clocks display, 12 hours or 24 hours can be set, if you phone is 12 hours clock display, then the fitness tracker is 16 hours clock display.</li></ul><br><div> <div> <h2>Product description</h2> <div> <div> <div> <div> <div> <div> <h4> Activity Monitoring All Day </h4> <p> This fitness tracker takes advanced to provide you activity data all-day experience. Don’t forget to check your data on \"H Band\" app , knowing your kids activity better. </p> </div> <div> <h4> Healthy Tracker Watch </h4> <p> Track your heart and blood pressure all day long and analyze the heart data,even during the workout.It can help you adjust your workout and keep health. </p> </div> <div> <h4> Activity Tracker Supports 11 Modes </h4> <p> This fitness watch records up to 11 sports to help you better track your workout,include swimming, Walking, Running, Cycling, Treadmill, Hiking, Fitness, Basketball,Badminton, Tennis, Football, Mountaineering, Spinning </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div> <div> <div> <div> <h4> Auto Sleep Monitoring </h4> <p> The fitness tracker will tracker your sleep trends. It can monitor light and deep sleep stages automatically at night. Get a better understanding of your sleep quality. </p> </div> <div> <h4> Sedentary Reminder </h4> <p> This smart band can remind you to relax when you sit and work for a long tome. Help you develop an energetic and healthy lifestyle. </p> </div> <div> <h4> Medication Reminder </h4> <p> Setting a reminder time in the APP that can take the medicine to remind kid to take the medicine on time. Continue to keep a friendly reminder, and speedy recovery. </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div> <div> <div> <div> <h4> Remote Camera Controller </h4> <p> This watch can remote control your phone\'s camera to capture the cherished moments.Just enjoy the time together.That way you can take a selfie without holding your phone. </p> </div> <div> <h4> IP68 Waterproof </h4> <p> Designed according to waterproof and dustproof standard, you can wear it when washing hands,swimming ( within 30 Mins ), but it can\'t wrist to take bath with hot water, diving. </p> </div> <div> <h4> Stopwatch </h4> <p> The stopwatch function make your every traningor workout counted. When you want to set the time for a fitness goal or need time reminding in daily life, the tracker can be used as a timer to optimize your traning effect. </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div>', 30.86, 10, '1766821228_694f8d6c473c0.jpg', NULL, '{\"Sport Type\":\"Cycling, Diving, Fitness, Running, Swimming, Walking\",\"Style\":\"Modern\",\"Screen Size\":\"0.96 Inches\",\"Operating System\":\"Android Wear 2.0\",\"Battery Capacity\":\"105 Milliamp Hours\",\"Battery Cell Composition\":\"Lithium Ion\",\"Color\":\"Pink\",\"Included Components\":\"1 x Smartwatch\",\"Shape\":\"Rectangular\",\"Package Weight\":\"0.11 Kilograms\",\"Item Weight\":\"0.11 Kilograms\",\"Connectivity Technology\":\"GPS\",\"Size\":\"N\",\"Wireless Communication Standard\":\"Infrared\",\"Standing screen display size\":\"0.96 Inches\",\"GPS\":\