(400, '6943f75e345b29bc885de34b', 'https://autods-scraper-images.s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/1c85216d9ea998e0bbabed68afe069c2.png', '4768370', NULL, 33, 'Fitness Tracker No Bluetooth No APP No Phone Needed, Fitness Watch for Men Women Parents IP68 Waterproof with Full Touch Screen Steps Calories Counter Sleep Tracker Alarm Clocks (Purple)', 'fitness-tracker-no-bluetooth-no-app-no-phone-needed-fitness-watch-for-men-women-parents-ip68-waterproof-with-full-touch-screen-steps-calories-counter-sleep-tracker-alarm-clocks-purple-ef4f88', 'new', 'c6549fa2-cfee-48df-bc1e-2c2932d958e8', 'Fitness Tracker No Bluetooth No APP No Phone Needed, Fitness Watch for Men Women Parents IP68 Waterproof with Full Touch Screen Steps Calories Counter Sleep Tracker Alarm Clocks (Purple)', NULL, '【Fitness Tracker Without Smartphone】No need to connect the fitness tracker to any smartphone. This No Bluetooth fitness tracker watch can work without Bluetoo...', '【Fitness Tracker Without Smartphone】No need to connect the fitness tracker to any smartphone. This No Bluetooth fitness tracker watch can work without Bluetooth or any App installation. It...', '<ul><li>【Fitness Tracker Without Smartphone】No need to connect the fitness tracker to any smartphone. This No Bluetooth fitness tracker watch can work without Bluetooth or any App installation. It will be a great gift for Elderly - They need a simple, easy to use fitness watch that can work without a cell phone.</li><li>【All-Day Activity Tracker】This fitness tracker can track your daily activities like steps, calories, walking distance, sleep duration. It has 2 kinds of practical sports modes including Running & Walking. Helping you to stay active and develop a healthy lifestyle.</li><li>【Fitness Tracker With Large Color Touchscreen】Unlike most traditional fitness trackers with just touch button, our fitness tracker featuring a large 1.47-inch TFT full-touch color screen with adjustable brightness, it ensures smooth using experience and clarity for you. With 5 built-in watch dials, this fitness watch suits for women and men.</li><li>【7 Days Battery Life & IP68 Waterproof Watch】 This fitness watch is charged through the magnetic charger. Our waterproof watches for women and men meets 7-days of normal use with about 2.5 hours of charging. With IP68 waterproof standard, no longer have to worry when you wear it while swimming or sweating out.</li><li>【More Practical Functions】This Non-Bluetooth fitness watch also has many useful built-in tools, like Alarm Clocks, Respiratory Training, Stopwatch, Timer, Drinking Water Reminder, Adjustable Brightness, Stretch Reminder, etc. You can get everything done without a smartphone.</li></ul><br><div> <div> <h2>Product description</h2> <div> <div> <div> <div> <div> <div> <h4> Non Bluetooth Fitness Tracker With Large Touchscreen </h4> <p> Unlike the other traditional Non-Bluetooth watches with only one touch button, our fitness tracker watch has a 1.47\" large TFT Touchscreen, which can provide smooth using experience for you. No longer need to spend time to figure out the complicated operation. </p> </div> <div> <h4> All-Day Activities Tracking </h4> <p> This activity tracker can record your daily steps, distance, calories burned data. It is also featuring with 2 sports modes: Running &amp; Walking. Helping you to stay motivated. </p> </div> <div> <h4> Fitness Tracker </h4> <p> This Non-Bluetooth fitness tracker is very user-friendly to the elderly. It is very comfortable to wear and easy to use, suitable for gift to your parents and friends. Helping them to stay active and stay healthy. </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div> <div> <div> <div> <h4> Sleep Tracker &amp; Alarm Clocks </h4> <p> This activity watch can record your sleep duration, it can help you to adjust and improve your sleep habits. You can add up to 10 alarm clocks on the watch to wake you up by gentle vibration. </p> <p> *Note: The sleep monitor is manually operated. </p> </div> <div> <h4> IP68 Waterproof Watch </h4> <p> With the IP68 waterproof standard for daily needs, this fitness tracker can be worn while running in the rain, or washing hands without any worry. But please don\'t wear it when hot bath, swimming, or diving. </p> </div> <div> <h4> More Useful Tools </h4> <p> This tracker has many useful functions, like Multilingual Support, Respiratory Training, Stopwatch &amp; Timer, Drinking Water Reminder, Adjustable Brightness, Stretch Reminder, etc. No longer be undistracted by smartphones. </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div> <div> <p> <span><u>We offer life-time after-sales &amp; replacement service. If there is any issue, please feel free to message us for help, we will give you the satisfactory solution.(Go to Your Order, Find the order ID in the list, Click \'Contact with us\')</u></span> </p> <p> <span>FAQ: Q1: How To Use?(Using Tips)</span> </p> <p> A. The watch has a full-touch screen, you can tap the screen to enable the function you want. </p> <p> B. Swipe the screen to the right to return to the previous page, it will also save the settings like alarm clocks, drink water reminder, sedentary reminder. </p> <p> C. The right side button: </p> <ul><li><span>It is the power button, you can long press it to turn on/off the watch.</span></li><li><span>Pressing this button can stop/continue the clock when you are using the timer/countdown.</span></li><li><span><span><u>*Note: This button will not save the settings.</u></span></span></li></ul> <p> <span>Q2: How To Make My Steps Data More Accurate？</span> </p> <ul><li><span>Please make sure the personal info is filled in the watch correctly to improve the accuracy.(Turn on the watch-&gt;Swipe down the screen to find the \"Settings\"-&gt;Personal Info-&gt;Fill in the Date of birth, Gender, Height, Weight, Step Length)</span></li><li><span>This watch has a built-in 3D gravity sensor, except the normal steps, it will also record as steps when you swing your arm to a certain extent. In order to lessen the error, the watch won\'t count if you walk within 10 steps. Understand how the steps counter works, you can better understand your steps data.</span></li></ul> <p> <span>Q3: How To Change/Save The Settings?</span> </p> <p> Please swipe the screen to the right to save the settings.(Pressing the right side button can only be back to the previous page) </p> <p> <span>Q4: How To Track The Sleep?</span> </p> <p> Please switch on the sleep function of watch before bed, turn it off when you wake up. The sleep monitor is manually operated. </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div>', 41.15, 10, '1766821235_694f8d73e31fb.jpg', NULL, '{\"Item model number\":\"S2\",\"Whats in the box\":\"Charging Cable, Fitness Tracker, User Manual\",\"Connectivity technologies\":\"Bluetooth\",\"Battery Cell Composition\":\"Lithium Polymer\",\"Department\":\"Unisex-Adult; Kids\",\"Other display features\":\"Wireless\",\"Battery Capacity\":\"140 Milliamp Hours\",\"Operating System\":\"Nein\",\"Wireless communication technologies\":\"Bluetooth\",\"Product Dimensions\":\"6.42 x 2.95 x 0.67 inches\",\"Battery Power Rating\":\"160\",\"Shape\":\"Rectangular\",\"Model Name\":\"S2\",\"Special features\":\"Activity Tracker, Alarm Clock\",\"Screen Size\":\"1.47 Inches\",\"Ram Memory Installed Size\":\"128 MB\",\"Item Weight\":\"1.02 ounces\",\"Connectivity Technology\":\"Bluetooth\",\"Human Interface Input\":\"Touchscreen\",\"Standing screen display size\":\"1.47 Inches\",\"Special Feature\":\"Activity Tracker, Alarm Clock\",\"GPS\":\"No GPS\",\"Weight\":\"29 Grams\",\"Color\":\"Purple\",\"Scanner Resolution\":\"172 x 320\",\"Batteries\":\"1 Lithium Polymer batteries required. (included)\",\"OS\":\"Nein\"}', 1, '2025-12-27 13:10:35', '2026-01-03 15:11:42'),
