(403, '695393ce1f79f0f0a0fba170', 'https://autods-scraper-images.s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/2fa54074d36bdf68465516cb18fc24b3.png', '4768370', NULL, 33, 'Amazon Essentials Women\'s High-Stretch Mid-Rise Skinny Jeans', 'amazon-essentials-womens-high-stretch-mid-rise-skinny-jeans-9e28ee', 'new', 'B0DX22GZXZ', 'Amazon Essentials Women\'s High-Stretch Mid-Rise Skinny Jeans', NULL, '  The Amazon Essentials Women\'s High-Stretch Mid-Rise Skinny Jeans are designed with both style and comfort in mind, making them a versatile addition to any war...', '  The Amazon Essentials Women\'s High-Stretch Mid-Rise Skinny Jeans are designed with both style and comfort in mind, making them a versatile addition to any wardrobe. These jeans feature a d...', '<div> <p> <span>The Amazon Essentials Women\'s High-Stretch Mid-Rise Skinny Jeans are designed with both style and comfort in mind, making them a versatile addition to any wardrobe. These jeans feature a dark wash that effortlessly pairs with a variety of tops, from casual tees to elegant blouses, making them suitable for both everyday wear and special occasions. The mid-rise fit provides a flattering silhouette while allowing for ease of movement, making them perfect for running errands, attending social gatherings, or simply lounging at home.</span> </p> <p> <span>Constructed with high-stretch fabric, these jeans ensure a comfortable fit that adapts to your body, providing all-day wear without compromising on style. Whether you\'re dressing them up with heels or keeping it casual with sneakers, the Amazon Essentials Women\'s High-Stretch Mid-Rise Skinny Jeans are designed to keep you looking chic and feeling great. Available in size 12 Short, these jeans cater to a range of body types, ensuring that every woman can enjoy the perfect fit.</span> </p> </div> \n<ul>\n  <li>High-stretch fabric for maximum comfort and flexibility</li>\n  <li>Mid-rise design for a flattering fit</li>\n  <li>Dark wash color for versatile styling options</l