(404, '6953cef101719ce5e182e1da', 'https://autods-scraper-images.s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/45d803b0e93bbe252af0b8fdd62984ef.png', '4768370', NULL, 33, 'Levi Strauss Signature Gold Women\'s Bootcut Shaping Jeans', 'levi-strauss-signature-gold-womens-bootcut-shaping-jeans-30a480', 'new', 'AUTODS-6953cef101719ce5e182e1da', 'Levi Strauss Signature Gold Women\'s Bootcut Shaping Jeans', NULL, '  Introducing the Levi Strauss Signature Gold Women\'s Bootcut Shaping Jeans, designed to provide both style and comfort for the modern woman. Crafted from premi...', '  Introducing the Levi Strauss Signature Gold Women\'s Bootcut Shaping Jeans, designed to provide both style and comfort for the modern woman. Crafted from premium super-stretch denim, these...', '<div> <p> <span>Introducing the Levi Strauss Signature Gold Women\'s Bootcut Shaping Jeans, designed to provide both style and comfort for the modern woman. Crafted from premium super-stretch denim, these jeans are engineered to smooth and contour your figure, ensuring a flattering silhouette. The innovative built-in tummy-smoothing panel offers gentle support, allowing you to feel confident and comfortable throughout the day. With classic 5-pocket styling, these jeans seamlessly blend fashion with functionality, making them a versatile addition to your wardrobe.</span> </p> <p> <span>The slim fit through the hip and thigh, combined with a stylish bootcut leg, makes these jeans perfect for various occasions, whether you\'re dressing up for a night out or keeping it casual for a weekend brunch. Pair them with your favorite blouse and heels for a chic look, or opt for a relaxed tee and sneakers for a more laid-back vibe. No matter how you style them, the Levi Strauss Signature Gold Women\'s Bootcut Shaping Jeans are sure to become a staple in your collection.</span> </p> </div>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>Premium super-stretch denim for optimal comfort and flexibility</li>\n  <li>Built-in tummy-smoothing panel for a flattering fit</li>\n  <li>Classic 5-pocket styling for practicality and timeless appeal</li>\n  <li>Slim fit through the hip and thigh with a stylish bootcut leg</li>\n  <li>Versatile design suitable for various occasions and easy to style</li>\n</ul>', 32.66, 10, '1768504356_69693c24a2134.jpg', NULL, '{\"Item model number\":\"94453-0009\",\"Color\":\"Blue Laguna-waterless\",\"Department\":\"womens\",\"Size\":\"12 Short\",\"Special Size\":\"Standard\",\"Manufacturer\":\"Signature by Levi Strauss & Co. Women\'s Apparel\"}', 1, '2026-01-16 00:42:36', '2026-03-07 15:40:39'),
