(412, '698c973e22639b7acb61ed05', 'https://autods-scraper-images.s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/5b66e6c47810ba070521e64687839212.png', '4768370', NULL, 33, 'Portable  B1 Wireless Label Maker Adhesive Sticker Printer Labeling Machine DIY 20-50Mm Labels for Office Home', 'portable-b1-wireless-label-maker-adhesive-sticker-printer-labeling-machine-diy-20-50mm-labels-for-office-home-bf4ae6', 'new', 'AUTODS-698c973e22639b7acb61ed05', 'Portable  B1 Wireless Label Maker Adhesive Sticker Printer Labeling Machine DIY 20-50Mm Labels for Office Home', NULL, 'Niimbot B1 Label Maker*Model: B1*Material: ABS*Color:Blue*Resolution: 203dpi*Printing speed: max 50mm/s*Print Width: 20-50 mm*Printing Technology: Thermal*Opera...', 'Niimbot B1 Label Maker*Model: B1*Material: ABS*Color:Blue*Resolution: 203dpi*Printing speed: max 50mm/s*Print Width: 20-50 mm*Printing Technology: Thermal*Operating temperature: 5~45℃*Batter...', '<div><p><br></p><div><p>Niimbot B1 Label Maker</p><p>*Model: B1<br>*Material: ABS<br>*Color:Blue<br>*Resolution: 203dpi<br>*Printing speed: max 50mm/s<br>*Print Width: 20-50 mm<br>*Printing Technology: Thermal<br>*Operating temperature: 5~45℃<br>*Battery-capacity: 1500mAh<br>*Charging interface: Type-c<br>*Charging time:4-5 hours<br>*Product size: 132*91.2*61.6mm<br>*Product net weight:293g<br>*Applicable industries: Home - living room, kitchen, bedroom，storage,supermarket,stores,clothing, jewellery, small business owners, office & home organization etc.</p></div><div><p>Package included:</p><p>1×Thermal Label Printer<br>1×Type-C cable<br>1×User Manual<br>1×Gift: 1 Roll Label Paper (Inside the printer)</p><div><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Sa29f4e54e9d04a6494268a37be76c6a0K.jpg\"></div></div><div><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/S64fb59104631449da496b6376d6cb15df.jpg\"></div><div><p>Size:</p><p>Product size: 132*91.2*61.6mm</p></div><div><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Sdb83461ca3b640d7901650827cea08f0s.jpg\"></div><div><p>USB Rechargeable</p><p>Mini printer is built in a 1500mAh Rechargeable Battery, which keep printing for 5 hours, and standby at least 1 week.</p><div><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Se8ab6ec60add492fbc383da0e29df831v.jpg\"></div></div><div><p>With thermal printing, , don’t need to buy ink, toner, or carbon tape.<br><br>Bluetooth Wireless Connection- compatible with iOS & Android,supports long distance printing with bluetooth</p></div><div><p>Inkless print</p><p>Direct thermal printing, no ink, toner, or ribbons.<br>Imported print head with unique thermal printing algorithm, clear printing.simply replace the label paper after used up.</p><div><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Sf6a7a67acf7c4b8baef5c81dc7c852c8v.jpg\"></div></div><div><p>Automatic Label Recognition</p><p>The Niimbot paper with RFID technology, the device will automatically identify the type of paper and select the template.<br><br>Automatic Label Recognition reads & selects label type</p></div><div><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Sd4f19a5788e94f8a8dfc1860cb164bb1l.jpg\"></div><div><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/S30481394e1bb4c10891257839166078dU.jpg\"></div><div><p>Printh width: 20-50mm/1-2 inch</p><p>The B1 label maker can print 20-50 mm width label ,can print product labels, address labels, ingredient labels, price labels, clothing labels, jewelry labels etc.</p></div><div><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Se00220bb414b4eb89c09a854f351869fL.jpg\"></div><div><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/S9e31b4d3c8a94d90a3f0a036f0d1d256f.jpg\"></div><div><p>Thermal Label</p><p>Waterproof, anti-oil, tear-resistant, scratch-resistant.</p></div><div><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/S503af75edb014d3a9ab46356da284168w.jpg\"></div><div><p>Multiple Creative Templates</p><p>This app of this stickers maker provides a variety of free templates, containing texts, tables, symbols, logos, barcodes, QR codes, images, time, insert Excel, etc. Easy to create various cute label stickers from your phone. Labels are fixed in length, not support continuous label tape.<br><br>Rich content, one \"print\" is complete, diversified printing content, time, one-dimensional code, two-dimensional code, picture, line, Chinese, English, Japanese and Korean, and other languages</p><div><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/S35ed7358778e4871bb5d72c43d82b192c.jpg\"><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/S1c97a3a185cd466a80d3653e41234306F.jpg\"></div></div><div><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/S8c09f01bb5da424da994a4e366f0cc3dN.jpg\"></div><div><p>3 intelligent recognition inputs</p><p>1 Speech recognition, you can type, label, or speak<br><br>2 Picture to text, the picture is automatically converted to text with high accuracy<br><br>3 Scan code recognition, convert the scanned barcode content into text or barcode, and copy to APP</p><div><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Sc5bf57cb8937495f8bfa848e17469d79J.jpg\"></div></div><div><p>Portable and Convenient:</p><p>Exquisite design,portable and mini size,easy to take and use</p><div><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/S6332d2a78cb54c1780cb0b311064b3eae.jpg\"></div></div><div><p>Wirelss connect:</p><p>Bluetooth link, get rid of the \"wire\" system, compatible with ios, Android, tablet, PC, and other devices, connection distance is up to 10m.</p><div><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/S041fbf2048664a16b689b6b1bc2462d4B.jpg\"></div></div><div><p>How to use?</p><p>Wireless mini label maker can print within 10-meter away from the smartphone connected by Bluetooth.<br><br>1 Download the App \"NIIMBOT\" from Apple Store/Google Play or by QR code from the manual.<br>2.Open the App and choose the B1 Series Printer. <br><br>3.Connect B1 printer in “NIIMBOT” App，not in system settings. <br><br>4.When loading the paper, please make sure the sticker side facing down. <br><br>5.When printing, please ensure that the printed content is within the red print box, otherwise the complete content will not be printed.</p><div><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/S26805abf3ebc4dadbba6d5e3cffa0ef1I.png\"></div></div><div><p>Widely Use:</p></div><div><p>for home and office</p><p>The label maker machines are used widely in organizing home supplies, classifying cosmetics items, price name jewelry tags, jar stickers, school and office files classification, storage, marking, etc. Perfect back-to-school item.</p></div><div><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Sb6d60febcd4841eca83480cdf4a092cab.png\"><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/S998fe4d84e8845f68afe805042e5577cx.png\"><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/S09218bc080454718b5cd054f535a0554c.png\"></div><div><p>for commercial use:</p><p>Small businesses: clothing, crafts, retail, jewelry etc. Labeling address, barcode, shipping, price, date, ingredients, logos labels for product.</p><div><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Se740eefb64974cbc9ffcb25669f68cffR.jpg\"></div></div><div><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/S2597a02c8d74492cb48bce347c436a48P.jpg\"><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Sb53eea0b84eb4e10a67570dbb37da28ex.jpg\"></div><div><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/S0b0fc21795604af08face4aaa8269f96F.jpg\"></div><p><br></p></div>', 44.10, 1, '1770822203_698c9a3b3e2b6.jpg', NULL, '{\"model\":\"B1\",\"battery included\":\"Yes\",\"interface type\":\"Bluetooth\",\"double-sided printing\":\"No\",\"type\":\"Pocket Printer\",\"paper feed mode\":\"Roll Feed\",\"print speed\":\"30ppm\",\"supports network printing\":\"Wired\\/Wireless\",\"high-concerned chemical\":\"None\",\"max paper size\":\"A8\",\"signal connection type\":\"Bluetooth\",\"origin\":\"Mainland China\",\"internal memory\":\"None\",\"black print speed\":\"15-30mm\\/s\",\"max resolution\":\"203dpi\",\"after-sale service\":\"Shop\'s Three Guarantees\",\"color\":\"None\",\"voltage\":\"100-240V\",\"application\":\"For Home Use\",\"weight\":\"1.5kg\",\"consumable type\":\"Label Paper\",\"dot matrix printer type\":\"Universal ticket printer\",\"certification\":\"weee\",\"use\":\"Label Maker\",\"item\":\"b