(419, '699c565005928f201ba5e98d', 'https://autods-scraper-images.s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/6052e108c9591adada9d2b84afa308e9.png', '4768370', NULL, 33, 'Cheap Farm Equipment Feed Machines Crushing Mixer 1T for Pig Cow Farm', 'cheap-farm-equipment-feed-machines-crushing-mixer-1t-for-pig-cow-farm-dc4b69', 'new', 'ea67e4b4-984a-4546-bee2-7786c33fbf1c', 'Cheap Farm Equipment Feed Machines Crushing Mixer 1T for Pig Cow Farm', NULL, ' Product Description product name:Cow/ chicken/horse/cattle feed mill equipment/grinder and Mixer/ Feed crushing Machine Horizontal spiral mixerVertical mixerPr...', ' Product Description product name:Cow/ chicken/horse/cattle feed mill equipment/grinder and Mixer/ Feed crushing Machine Horizontal spiral mixerVertical mixerProduct application objects: rab...', '<div> <div><div>Product Description</div></div> <div><div><div><div><div><div><b>product name:</b>Cow/ chicken/horse/cattle feed mill equipment/grinder and Mixer/ Feed crushing Machine Horizontal spiral mixerVertical mixer<br><b>Product application objects: </b>rabbits, cows, chickens, sheep, horses, geese, donkeys, ducks, dogs, quail, pigs, pigeons, mules<br><b>Product use: </b>feed machinery<br><b>Product size: </b>1370*1240*2650mm (customizable)<br><b>Product packaging:</b> film<br><b>Product specifications: </b>0.5t/1t/1.5t//2tper hour<br><b>Product introduction:</b><br>Feed crushing mixer is mainly composed of feed crusher, feed mixer, base, feeding structure, etc. It has simple structure, novel style, reliable performance, stable operation, convenient maintenance, high production efficiency, small floor space, time-saving and labor-saving, suitable for Feed processing in large, medium and small farms and individual livestock farmers (such as processed feed for pigs, cattle, chickens, ducks, etc.).<br>Compared with the previous feed mixer, the feed crushing mixer has a small footprint, convenient transportation, higher efficiency and better sealing. The vertical feed crushing and mixing machine is a mixing machine that can be used for both crushing and mixing.</div></div></div></div></div></div> <div><div><table><tbody><tr><td><div><div>Model</div></div></td><td><div><div>500type</div></div></td><td><div><div>1000type</div></div></td><td><div><div>1500type</div></div></td><td><div><div>2000type</div></div></td></tr><tr><td><div><div>Crushing power</div></div></td><td><div><div>7.5kw</div></div></td><td><div><div>7.5kw</div></div></td><td><div><div>11kw</div></div></td><td><div><div>15kw</div></div></td></tr><tr><td><div><div>Mixer power</div></div></td><td><div><div>3kw</div></div></td><td><div><div>4kw</div></div></td><td><div><div>5.5kw</div></div></td><td><div><div>5.5kw</div></div></td></tr><tr><td><div><div>Dimensions</div></div></td><td><div><div>2450*1110*1900mm</div></div></td><td><div><div>2800*1300*2300mm</div></div></td><td><div><div>2800*1650*2300</div></div></td><td><div><div>2800*1700*2600mm</div></div></td></tr><tr><td><div><div>Hourly output</div></div></td><td><div><div>0.5t/h</div></div></td><td><div><div>1t/h</div></div></td><td><div><div>1.5t/h</div></div></td><td><div><div>2t/h</div></div></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div> <div><div>FAQ</div></div> <div><div><div><h3><span><font>Frequently Asked Questions:</font></span></h3><div><div><div> <b>Q: Who are we? </b> A: We are based in Henan, China, Zhengzhou Jinhui Agricultural S&T Co., Ltd. was established in 2011, and GREAT FARM is its subsidiary brand. <b>Q: How can we guarantee quality? </b>A: Always a pre-production sample before mass production; Always final Inspection before shipment; <b>Q: What can you buy from us? </b>A: Our company is committed to the production and sale of livestock farming equipment, focusing on providing one-stop solutions for animal breeding farms such as poultry farm, cattle farm, sheep farm, and pig farm. <i><b>The equipment we provide includes four categories: </b></i>1. Steel processing, such as chicken cages, quail cages, and livestock